<component type="desktop-application">

  <id>io.github.city_of_memphis_wastewater.copy_n_launch_xlsx</id>

  <name>Copy n Launch XLSX</name>

  <summary>Copy, rename, and launch spreadsheets for daily data entry</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Copy n Launch XLSX is a GUI tool for automating daily spreadsheet workflows.
      It copies a template Excel file, applies standardized naming with dates,
      and opens the resulting file for immediate data entry.
    </p>

    <p>
      It is designed for operational environments where consistent spreadsheet
      generation and predictable file structure are required.
    </p>

    <p>
      The tool includes both a graphical interface and a CLI for automation.
    </p>
  </description>

